data.description: Come live the country life in White Mountain Lake.    Situated on 2 acres (Approx 87,120 sf) this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom split floorplan home is what you have been looking for:  Spacious living area with a cozy fireplace, plenty of windows throughout for tons of natural light,  large kitchen with ample cabinet space, large master suite with a garden tub, dual vanities, and roomy closet.  The second and third bedrooms are generous in size.   Outside is a metal 2 car garage and carport.    Animal enclosures are in place for your chickens and 4-legged family members.   Close proximity to Bourbon Ranch Road for easy access.   Private well with recently installed pump and new lines,  for your water needs.   Come take a look today!
